OpenClinica:Section.SectionInstructions: <script src="includes/jmesa/jquery.min.js">// for OC versions before 3.1.4, use jquery-1.3.2.min.js !</script> <script lang="Javascript"> $.noConflict(); jQuery(document).ready(function($){ var dobField = $("#DateOfBirth").parent().parent().find("input"); var signField = $("#OtherDate").parent().parent().find("input"); var ageField = $("#CalculatedAge").parent().parent().find("input"); ageField.attr("readonly", true); var months = ["jan", "feb", "mar", "apr", "may", "jun", "jul", "aug", "sep", "oct", "nov", "dec"]; function calcYearsBetween(startDate, startMonth, endDate, endMonth) { var years = (endDate.getFullYear() - startDate.getFullYear()); if (endMonth < startMonth || endMonth == startMonth && endDate.getDate() < startDate.getDate()) years--; return years; } function parseDate(input){ var parts = input.split("-"); var myDate = new Date(); myDate.setFullYear(parts[2]); myDate.setDate(parts[0]); return myDate; } function getNumMonth(dateInput){ var parts = dateInput.split("-"); var charMonth = parts[1].toLowerCase(); return months.indexOf(charMonth); } function yearsBetween(){ var dob = dobField.val(); var sign = signField.val(); var age=""; var curAge = ageField.val(); if(dob!=="" && sign!==""){ age = String(calcYearsBetween(parseDate(dob), getNumMonth(dob), parseDate(sign), getNumMonth(sign))); } if(curAge!==age){ ageField.val(age); ageField.change(); } } dobField.blur(function(){ yearsBetween(); }); signField.blur(function(){ yearsBetween(); }); $("#srl").on("focus", function () { yearsBetween(); }); $("#srh").on("focus", function () { yearsBetween(); }); }); </script>

OpenClinica:StudyDescriptionAndStatus.OfficialTitle: A Multi-Site, Randomized, Single-blind, Placebo Controlled Trial of JUNO in Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus
OpenClinica:StudyDescriptionAndStatus.OpenClinica:DetailedDescription: This study will evaluate the safety, efficacy, and pharmacokinetics of JUNO given once daily compared to placebo and another diabetes drug in participants with Type 2 diabetes mellitus (T2DM).

OpenClinica:ConditionsAndEligibility.OpenClinica:Keywords: Diabetes, T2DM, Diabetes Mellitus, Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus
OpenClinica:ConditionsAndEligibility.OpenClinica:EligibilityCriteria: Fluent in English; Fasting plasma glucose ≤ 240 mg/dL (13.3 mmol/L; Hemoglobin A1c between 8% to 10%; Able to provide Informed Consent; Diagnosed with Type II diabetes mellitus for at least 24 months; At least 18 years of age
